ARGUMENT.

What is the tars' misdemeanour ? Plundering a Leith sloop, and making free with the Falernian in the casks. Citizens ashore call this a crime, but the sailor has been a freebooter from long ago—yffi, from the beginning. Witness the rogues the Argonauts‚ and yet the Argo is now a constellation of the heavenly sphere. Minerva herself gives to prudence the prize reft by means of freebooting.
